abstract: Australian diplomatic office in Kenya warns of possible pending terrorist attack in Nairobi.
lead_paragraph: The alert from the Australian diplomatic branch in Kenya follows a similar advisory two days ago from the United States about neighboring Uganda.

headline.main: Australia Warns of Terror Threat in Kenyan Capital
headline.print_headline: World Briefing | Africa; Kenya: Australia Warns of Possible Terrorist Attack
